 大纲-hugo建站
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%e5%a4%a7%e7%ba%b2-hugo%e5%bb%ba%e7%ab%99"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-hugo-建站教程记录"&gt;
 1. hugo 建站教程记录
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#1-hugo-%e5%bb%ba%e7%ab%99%e6%95%99%e7%a8%8b%e8%ae%b0%e5%bd%95"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1bovfeaEtQ" rel="noopener"&gt;b站24年视频教程&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a href="https://letere-gzj.github.io/hugo-stack/p/hugo/custom-blog/" rel="noopener"&gt;对应文字教程&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/" rel="noopener"&gt;hugo官网&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="11-创建-hugo-项目"&gt;
 1.1. 创建 hugo 项目
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#11-%e5%88%9b%e5%bb%ba-hugo-%e9%a1%b9%e7%9b%ae"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hugo new site dll-notes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Congratulations! Your new Hugo project was created in Z:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\d&lt;/span&gt;lliang14&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\O&lt;/span&gt;bsidian&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\m&lt;/span&gt;yNote&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\d&lt;/span&gt;ll-notes.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Just a few more steps...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;1. Change the current directory to Z:&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\d&lt;/span&gt;lliang14&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\O&lt;/span&gt;bsidian&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\m&lt;/span&gt;yNote&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;\d&lt;/span&gt;ll-notes.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;2. Create or install a theme:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - Create a new theme with the command &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hugo new theme &amp;lt;THEMENAME&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - Or, install a theme from https://themes.gohugo.io/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;3. Edit hugo.toml, setting the &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;theme&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; property to the theme name.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;4. Create new content with the command &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hugo new content &amp;lt;SECTIONNAME&amp;gt;\&amp;lt;FILENAME&amp;gt;.&amp;lt;FORMAT&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;5. Start the embedded web server with the command &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hugo server --buildDrafts&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="12-测试-hugo"&gt;
 1.2. 测试 hugo
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#12-%e6%b5%8b%e8%af%95-hugo"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd dll-notes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hugo server -D
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Built in &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;15&lt;/span&gt; ms
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Environment: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;development&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Serving pages from disk
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Running in Fast Render Mode. For full rebuilds on change: hugo server --disableFastRender
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Web Server is available at http://localhost:1313/ &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;bind address 127.0.0.1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Press Ctrl+C to stop
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 出现 Page Not Found 说明hugo正常 下一步安装主题&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="13-安装配置-hugo-主题"&gt;
 1.3. 安装配置 hugo 主题
